    "code": "012", 
    "data": "اَشْهَدُ اَنْ لاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللهُ وَحْدَهُ لاَ شَرِيْكَ لَهٗ \nASH-HADO AN LAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHO WAHDAHU LAA SHAREEKA LAHU \nI testify that there is no god save Allah; He is One; there is no associate (partner) with Him. \nوَ اَشْهَدُ اَنَّكَ رَسُوْلُهٗ وَ اَنَّكَ مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللهِ \nWA ASH-HADO ANNAKA RASOOLOHU WA ANNAKA MOHAMMADUBNO A’BDIL LAAHE \nI testify that you are His Apostle, and you are Mohammad son of Abdullah; \nوَ اَشْهَدُ اَنَّكَ قَدْ بَلَّغْتَ رِسَالاَتِ رَبِّكَ وَ نَصَحْتَ لِاُمَّتِكَ \nWA ASH-HADO ANNAKA QAD BALLAGHTA RESAALAATE RABBEKA WA NASAHTA LEUMMATEKA \nand I testify that you had delivered the Message of your Lord, advised and warned your followers (Ummah) like a sincere friend, \nوَ جَاهَدْتَ فِیْ سَبِيْلِ اللهِ بِالْحِکْمَةِ وَ الْمَوْعِظَة الْحَسَنَةِ \nWA JAAHADTA FEE SABEELIL LAAHE BILHIKMATE WAL MAWE’ZATIL HASANATE \nand strived, leaving no stone unturned, against heavy odds, in the cause of Allah, with wisdom, \nوَ اَدَّيْتَ الَّذِیْ عَلَيْكَ مِنَ الْحَقِّ \nWA ADDAYTAL LAZEE A’LAYKA MENAL HAQQE \nand good advice you performed that which were entrusted with by Allah \nوَ اَنَّكَ قَدْ رَؤُٔفْتَ بِالْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ وَ غَلَظْتَ عَلَی الْكَافِرِيْنَ \nWA ANNAKA QAD RAOOFTA BILMOMENEENA WA GHALAZTA A’LAL KAAFEREEN \n(and) you had been kind and compassionate to the believers, (but) was harsh with the disbelievers, \nوَ عَبَدْتَ اللهَ مُخْلِصًا حَتّٰی اَتٰيكَ الْيَقِيْنُ \nWA A’BADTAL LAAHA MUKHLESAN HATTAA ATAAKAL YAQEENO \nand had sincerely served Allah, till the inevitable (what was certain) came unto you. \nفَبَلَغَ اللهُ بِكَ اَشْرَفِ مَحَلِّ الْمُكَرَّمِيْنَ \nFABALAGHAL LAAHO BEKA ASHRAFA MAHALLIL MOKARRAMEENA \nSo Allah made you reach the highest stage of glory and honour. \nاَلْحَمْدُ لِلّٰهِ الَّذِیْ اسْتَنْقَذَنَا بِكَ مِنَ الشِّرْكِ وَ الضَّلاَلَةِ \nALHAMDOLIL LAAHIL LAZEES TANQAZANAA BEKA MENASH SHIRKE WAZ ZALAALATE \n(All) praise is for Allah (only) who saved us through you from the polytheism and going astray.\nاَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَ اٰلِهٖ \nALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADINW WA AALEHI\nO Allah! Send blessings on Mohammad and on his children. \nوَ اجْعَلْ صَلَوَاتِكَ وَ صَلَوَاتِ مَلآَئِكَتِكَ \nWAJ A’L SALAWAATEKA WA SALAWAATE MALAAEKATEKA \nYour blessings, and invocations of Your Angels, \nوَ اَنْبِيَائِكَ الْمُرْسَلِيْنَ وَ عِبَادِكَ الصَّالِحِيْنَ \nWA AMBEYAAEKA WALMURSALEEN WA E’BAADEKAS SAALEHEENA \n(of) Your Prophets and Apostles, (of) Your pious servants, \nوَ اَهْلِ السَّمَوَاتِ وَ الْاَرَضِيْنَ \nWA AHLIS SAMAAWAATE WAL ARAZEEN \n(of) the people of the heavens and the earths, \nوَ مَنْ سَبَّحَ لَكَ يَا رَبَّ الْعَالَمِيْنَ مِنَ الْاَوَّلِيْنَ وَ الْاٰخِرِيْنَ \nWA MAN SABBAHA LAKA YAA RABBAL A’ALAMEEN MENAL AWWALEENA WAL AAKHEREEN \nand (of) those who glorify You, (O the Lord of the worlds), from among the ancient and the present, \nعَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ عَبْدِكَ وَ رَسُوْلِكَ وَ نَبِيِّكَ وَ اَمِيْنِكَ \nA’LAA MOHAMMADIN A’BDEKA WA RASOOLEKA WA NABIYYEKA WA AMEENEKA \nbe on Mohammad, Your servant and Apostle Your Prophet Your confidant, \nوَ نَجِيِّكَ وَ حَبِيْبِكَ وَ صَفِيِّكَ وَصِفْوَتِكَ وَ خَاصَّتِكَ \nWA NAJEEBEKA WA HABEEBEKA WA SAFIYYEKA WA SIFWATEKA WA KHAASSATEKA \nYour volunteer, Your intimate friend, sincerely attached to You, purified by You, Your favorite, \nوَ خَالِصَتِكَ وَ خِيَرَتِكَ مِنْ خَلْقِكَ \nWA KHAALESATEKA WA KHEYARATEKA MIN KHALQEKA \nthe best essence from You, chosen in preference by You from Your creation,\nوَ اَعْطِهِ الْفَضْلَ وَ الْفَضِيْلَةَ وَالْوَسِيْلَةَ وَ الدَّرَجَةَ الرَّفِيْعَةَ \nWA AA’TEHIL FAZLA WAL FAZEELATA WAL WASEELATA WADDARAJATAR RAFEEA’TA\nand gave him surpassing superiority and eminence in wisdom and character, subtle ways and means, highest stations, \nوَ ابْعَثْهُ مَقَامًا مَحْمُوْداً يَغْبِطُهٗ بِهِ الْاَوَّلُوْنَ وَ الْاٰخِرُوْنَ \nWABA’SHO MAQAAMAM MAHMOODAN YAGHBETOHU BEHIL AWWALOONA WAL AAKHEROONA \nand put him on the pedestal of (praiseworthy) fame and fortune; found his position enviable the men of old and the men of later time. \nاَللّٰهُمَّ اِنَّكَ قُلْتَ وَ لَوْ اَنَّهُمْ اِذْ ظَلَمُوْا اَنْفُسَهُمْ \nALLAAHUMMA INNAKA QULTA WA LAW ANNAHUM IZZALAMOO ANFOSAHUM \nO Allah. You said: “And if, when they had wronged themselves, they had \nجَآئُوْكَ فَاسْتَغْفَرُوْا اللهَ وَ اسْتَغْفَرَ لَهُمُ الرَّسُوْلُ \nJAAAOOO-KA FASTAGHFARUL LAAHA WASTAGHFARA LAHOMUR RASOOLO \nbut come unto you and asked forgiveness of Allah, and asked forgiveness of the Apostle, \nلَوَجَدُوْا اللهَ تَوَّابًا رَّحِيْمًا \nLAWAJADUL LAAHA TAWWAABAR RAHEEMAN \nthey would have found Allah Forgiving, Merciful.” \nاِلٰهِیْ فَقَدْ اَتَيْتُ نَبِيَّكَ مُسْتَغْفِرًا \nELAAHI FAQAD ATAYTO NABIYYAKA MUSTAGHFERAN \nO my Allah, therefore I turn repentant to Your Prophet (s.a.), \nتَآئِباً مِنْ ذُنُوْبِیْ فَصَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَ اٰلِهٖ \nTAAEBAN MIN ZONOOBEE FASALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALEHI \nasking pardon for my sins, (so send blessings on Mohammad and on his children), \nوَ اغْفِرْ هَالِیْ يَا سَيِّدَنَا اَتَوَجَّهُ بِكَ \nWAGH FIR HAALEE YAA SAYYEDANAA ATAWAJJAHO BEKA \nand he kind to me. O our chief direct yourself, \nوَ بِاَهْلِ بَيْتِكَ اِلَی اللهِ تَعَالٰی رَبِّكَ وَ رَبِّیْ لِيَغْفِرَ لِیْ\nWA BEAHLEBAYTEKA ELAL LAAHE TA-A’ALAA RABBEKA WA RABBEE LEYAGHFERA LEE\nand your household towards the Most praised Allah, Your Lord and my Lord, in the matter of my request for forgiveness.\nSay 3 times:\nاِنَّ للهِ وَ اِنَّا اِلَيْهِ رَاجِعُوْنَ.\nINNAA LILLAAHE WA INNAA ELAYHE RAAJEO’ON\nVerily we are Allah’s; and verily unto Him shall we return.\nThen recite:\nاُصِبْنَا بِكَ يَا حَبِيْبَ قُلُوْبِنَا \nOSIBNAA BEKA YAA HABEEBA QOLOOBENAA \nWith love and longing for you, we move, O dearest friend, in your direction, \nفَمَا اَعْظَمَ الْمُصِيْبَةَ بِكَ حَيْثُ انْقَطَعَ عَنَّا الْوَحْیُ \nFAMAAA A’ZAMAL MOSEEBATA BEKA HAYSUN QATA-A’ A’NNAL WAHYO \nbecause the misery has increased, since revelation has been cutoff, \nوَ حَيْثُ فَقَدْ نَاكَ فَاِنَّا للهِ وَ اِنَّا اِلَيْهِ رَاجِعُوْنَ \nWA HAYSO FAQAD NAAKA FAINNAA LILLAAHE WA INNAA ELAYHE RAAJEO’ON \nand we lost you. Verily we are Allah’s; and verily unto Him shall we return. \nيَا سَيِّدَنَا يَا رَسُوْلَ اللهِ صَلَوَاتُ اللهِ عَلَيْكَ \nYAA SAYYEDANAA YAA RASOOLAL LAAHE SALAWAATUL LAAHE A’LAYKA \nO our Chief! O our Apostle of Allah! Blessings of Allah be on you and on the pure \nوَ عَلٰی اٰلِ بَيْتِكَ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ \nWA A’LAA AALEBAYTEKAT TAAHEREENA \nand pious people of your house. \nهٰذَا يَوْمُ السَّبْتِ وَ هُوَ يَوْمُكَ \nHAAZAA YAWMUS SABTE WA HOWA YAWMOKA \nToday is Saturday, your day, \nوَ اَنَا فِيْهِ ضَيْفُكَ وَ جَارُكَ \nWA ANAA FEEHE ZAYFOKA WA JAAROKA \nand I, in its hours, take refuge with you; seek your nearness, \nفَاَضِفْنِیْ وَ اَجِرْنِیْ فَاِنَّكَ كَرِيْمٌ \nFA-AZIFNEE WA AJIRNEE FA-INNAKA KAREEMUN \n(so) receive me with open arms, let me be near you, \nتُحِبُّ الضِّيَافَةَ وَ مَاْمُوْرٌ بِالْاِجَارَةِ \nTOHIBBUZ ZEYAAFATA WA MAAMOORUN BILEJAARATA \nbecause you are very kind, love to be hospitable, chosen and assigned to given asylum and refuge, \nفَاَضِفْنِیْ وَ اَحْسِنْ ضِيَافَتِیْ \nFAAZIFNEE WA-AHSIN ZEYAAFATEE \n(therefore) make me feel at home, amost generous friendly welcome, \nوَ اَجِرْنَا وَ اَحْسِنْ اِجَارَتَنَا \nWA-AJIRNAA WA-AHSIN EJAARATANAA \ntake us under your shelter, a most reliable protection; \nبِمَنْزِلَةِ اللهِ عِنْدَكَ وَ عِنْدَ اٰلِ بَيْتِكَ \nBEMANZELATIL LAAHE I’NDAKA WA I’NDA AALEBAYTEKA \nin the name for the sake of your belief in Allah, and your AhlulBayt’s belief in Him, \nوَ بِمَنْزِلَتِهِمْ عِنْدَهُ وَ بِمَا اسْتَوْدَعَکُمْ مِنْ عِلْمِهٖ \nWA BEMANZELATEHIM I’NDAHU WA BEMASTAWDA-A’KUM MIN I’LMEHI \nand the status He has assigned to them, whereby you (all) took into your keeping His Wisdom. \nفَاِنَّهُ اَکْرَمُ الْاَکْرَمِيْنَ.\nFAINNAHU AKRAMUL AKRAMEEN.\nVerily He is the most kind of all who show kindness.", 
    "title": "Ziyarah of Holy Prophet (s) on Saturday"
}